Title: Bogomol'nyi equations for solitons in Maxwell-Chern-Simons gauge

theories with the magnetic moment interaction termAuthors: Taejin Lee and Hyunsoo Min

Comments: 9 pages, Revtex, SNUTP-94/65

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D50 (1994) 7738-7741

Without assuming rotational invariance, we derive Bogomol'nyi equations forthe solitons in the abelian Chern-Simons gauge theories with the anomalousmagnetic moment interaction. We also evaluate the number of zero modes around astatic soliton configuration.